{"tid":950520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我女朋友成日呷我家姐醋","createTime":"2018-12-21T14:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T15:05:27.000Z","uid":123180,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bf52f24c78dfa31c38efcc7cca14942981271017","tid":950520,"uid":123180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"我同家姐由於年紀相若 所以由細到大都玩得好埋 早幾個月識左個女朋友 拍左拖無耐就帶左佢上黎屋企玩 返到屋企習慣性叫左句家姐之後就過去攬一攬佢 點知我女朋友見到就即刻黑曬口面<br />\n<br />\n之後有次夏天佢上黎我屋企 見到我家姐喺屋企著件吊帶背心加條屋企著嗰啲短褲 佢趁我去廁所嘅時候竟然同我家姐講：得你細佬喺度姐 使唔使著到咁博啊？<br />\n<br />\n其實我屋企道廁所門唔太隔音 所以我喺入面聽得一清二楚 但因為我真係好鐘意個女仔 所以我最後扮聽唔到 究竟我要點做先可以改變佢地既關係？"},{"pid":"662613e896dd66b47c91760a3c6b84cd8fbcc9ec","tid":950520,"uid":17474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:58:09.000Z","msg":"無圖點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dcede2e6b680bb5960fb396adb312d959117386","tid":950520,"uid":183878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:58:46.000Z","msg":"等我黎解決你家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff2cd66e7ddd1b46a44b5389fda3ec7bb484984","tid":950520,"uid":177660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"你條女咁閪嘅"},{"pid":"a98558feba46d868eb5a2df77ff8bd357e6dd94a","tid":950520,"uid":67903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/946608/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/946608/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n抄post?"},{"pid":"7e3f7ba73411301d047f1543e71354605c163acd","tid":950520,"uid":173078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"乜角色扮演真係咁好玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fb47767b322fb7dbc9d34f7b4118b215f6f684","tid":950520,"uid":11154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"終於有男朋友version<img src=\"/as